README

SUMMARY
-------

The coupler is a package for parallel data transfer between arbitrary physics 
codes. Interfaces are provided for data access to each physics. See doxygen
documentation for more developer details.


DEPENDENCIES
------------

The coupler has direct dependecies on the following Trilinos packages:

*: Teuchos
*: Tpetra

For parallel operations, there is an optional dependency on MPI. Both OpenMPI 
and MPICH2 implementations have been tested with this package.

CONFIGURE and BUILD
-------------------

The coupler uses the TriBITS cmake build system. See doc/build_notes/ for a 
sample configure script and additional configure/build documentation.


TEST
----

ctest - Run package the unit tests when enabled.